{"content":"<li class=\"n-box-item date-title\" data-end=\"1471233599\" data-start=\"1471147200\" data-txt=\"Sunday, December 22, 2019\">Sunday, August 14, 2016</li><li class=\"n-box-item sa-box-item\" data-id=\"3203185\" data-ts=\"1471215816\"><div class=\"media media-overflow-fix\"><div class=\"media-left\"><a class=\"box-ticker\" href=\"/symbol/PPS\" target=\"_blank\">PPS</a></div><div class=\"media-body\"><h4 class=\"media-heading\"><a href=\"/news/3203185-wsj-mid-america-apartment-nears-deal-for-post-properties\" sasource=\"on_the_move_news_fidelity\" target=\"_blank\">WSJ: Mid-America Apartment nears deal for Post Properties</a></h4><ul>\n<li>A deal for about $4B <a href=\"http://www.wsj.com/articles/maa-nears-deal-to-buy-post-properties-for-about-4-billion-1471210303\" target=\"_blank\">could be announced as soon as tomorrow</a>, according to the <em>Journal's</em> sources, with Post (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PPS\" title=\"Post Properties Inc.\">PPS</a>) owners set to receive 0.71 share of newly-issued <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MAA\" title=\"Mid-America Apartment Communities Inc.\">MAA</a> stock for each share of Post they hold.</li>\n<li>Based on MAA's Friday close of $102.15, this would mean about $72.53 for each share of Post - roughly a <font color=\"green\">16% premium</font> to Friday's close.</li>\n<li>Apartment landlords have naturally benefitted from the aftermath of the housing bust, but rent growth has begun to slow of late, leaving managements looking to mergers as the next way to drive value. Real estate is this year's 2nd busiest sector for M&amp;A activity with more than $215B of deals, including $52B among REITs.</li>\n</ul><div class=\"tiny-share-widget\" data-id=\"3203185\" data-linked=\"WSJ: Mid-America Apartment nears deal for Post Properties\" data-tweet=\"$PPS $PPS $MAA - WSJ: Mid-America Apartment nears deal for Post Properties https://seekingalpha.com/news/3203185-wsj-mid-america-apartment-nears-deal-for-post-properties?source=tweet\" data-url=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/3203185-wsj-mid-america-apartment-nears-deal-for-post-properties\"><div class=\"icon share-btn c-email\" title=\"Email a friend\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"icon share-btn c-twitter\" title=\"Share on Twitter\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"icon share-btn c-facebook\" title=\"Share on Facebook\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"icon share-btn c-linkedin\" title=\"Share on Linkedin\">&nbsp;</div></div><span class=\"mc_gray_separator\">|</span>  7:03 PM <span class='mc_gray_separator'>|</span> <span class='comments-n'><span class='comments-container '>1&nbsp;<span class='comments-number'>Comment</span></span></span></div></div></li>","count":1,"message":null,"success":true,"today":{"start":1576990800,"end":1577077199,"str":"Sunday, December 22, 2019"},"yesterday":{"start":1576904400,"end":1576990799}}